snippet.title: Transylmania II: The Vampire Bites Back! (2006) - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Full playthrough of Transylmania II, sequel to the online game originally published on Zeeks and Funschool.
This is the revised version with tutorial containers. Had to redo levels 6 and 7 because I died.

Original 2006 Version Playthrough: https://youtu.be/Fxayz5jAoWQ

#vampire #zeeks #funschool #kaboose #playthrough #nostalgia #flashgames
